com.sun.tools.visualvm.tools.jvmstat
Class JvmJvmstatModel

java.lang.Object
  com.sun.tools.visualvm.core.model.Model
      com.sun.tools.visualvm.tools.jvmstat.JvmJvmstatModel

public abstract class JvmJvmstatModel
extends Model

This class encapsulates information available via Jvmstat counters. It is preferred to use this class to get access to java home, total loaded classes, number of running threads etc. The advantage is that user code does not depend on particular counter name, which can be different for different JVM.

Author:
Tomas Hurka
